text: Rosebudd's Revenge is the fourth studio album by Roc Marciano. It was released on February 21, 2017 by Marci Enterprises. The album was produced by The Arch Druids, Mushroom Jesus, Modus Op, Knxwledge Animoss and Roc Marciano. Features guest appearances by his frequent collaborators Ka and Knowledge the Pirate. == Critical reception == ===Accolades=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! Publication ! Accolade !
